Rin_neg2 curr_neg2 0 1.0
R1_pos2 curr_pos2 pos2 499.0
R1_neg2 curr_neg2 neg2 499.0
R2_neg2 neg2 out2_pre 499000.0
R2_pos2 pos2 0 499000.0

* 理想运放模型
* 使用高增益比较反相端和同相端的电压差
Eopamp2 out2_pre 0 pos2 neg2 1000000000.0
